---
// hero — a scene reel: three slices of the work, a few seconds each, crossfading
// on an 18s loop. 1) the model catalog as a living matrix — a scanline sweeps,
// changes blip accent. 2) a multiplex bundle — streams pinch through one node
// and cross over; a token rides the accent path. 3) a dependency cascade — an
// accent root fans through uneven layers to a sink, activity tracing the edges.
// Progress ticks along the bottom mark the sequence. Decorative: currentColor
// + accent, surface fills. Reduced motion holds on the static matrix.
---

